{"tid":1465663,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"共狗一日就打殘左機場呢張王牌","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:14:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T00:50:10.000Z","uid":171704,"like":26,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"e7af9a243afc5d78c9b750e17eb7385d720c018a","tid":1465663,"uid":171704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:14:28.000Z","msg":"放兩件個樣一睇就知係大陸佬既黎扮鬼<br />\n俾你捉到之後鬼咁冷靜冇還過手任你搞足幾粒鐘都冇狗黎有哂noise<br />\n仲帶齊哂証件同件tee黎俾你搵到牽動現場情緒<br />\n<br />\n聽日就有哂料大做新聞蓋左811<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後想講<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">612 721 811</span>"},{"pid":"7e8dc1fa78431ff1f327faf2ec368a6c1e769eca","tid":1465663,"uid":60321,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:15:40.000Z","msg":"依家都要預左個個星期都係咁比人分化架喇<br />\n唔好以為得我地有妙計 敵人都一樣有妙計<br />\n唔好以為有必勝方法 好多時最後都係講堅持<br />\n<br />\n總之鬧完交就繼續出黎 繼續做自己認為啱既事<br />\n到星期六日大家又如常出返哂黎 滿返士氣<br />\n<br />\n始終人多 就算無鬼 都要學識面對有人犯錯有人鬧交<br />\n唔係所有野都到自己控制 但你控制到自己繼續出黎<br />\n<br />\n記住不分化 大家係一team人 <br />\n唔好輕敵 的確係難打 但唔好灰心 繼續加油"},{"pid":"6bead6ddf00319070e572ba54906ef3a4973e2d6","tid":1465663,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:15:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"03493807320ea320c6ca7dd5933b60f735ae9d41","tid":1465663,"uid":271051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:16:17.000Z","msg":"Agger"},{"pid":"3ad8f8ddfa91af5ed84e385f3709007ebe4dd366","tid":1465663,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:16:24.000Z","msg":"811未消化完 整單咁既野 都幾難拆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35b2ede8d3fdf068e59ceb9850931a5848f6ff17","tid":1465663,"uid":231583,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:16:40.000Z","msg":"你地再個個開post講機場呢張牌玩完咪真係玩完<br />\n冷處理，集齊人，再入過去咪得<br />\n唔好自亂陣腳先"},{"pid":"cb2d60dc87e1aaab2defdc7823cbcfe0a26df46f","tid":1465663,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:16:50.000Z","msg":"唔玩cancel 玩<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">delay</span></span></strong>!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464220\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464220</a><br />\n<br />\n屌你地老母 你地有無搭過飛機架？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464168\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464168</a><br />\n<br />\n機場現時既建議方法，希望多人睇到<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464007\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464007</a><br />\n<br />\n8.13機場策略<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1463429\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1463429</a><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：機場人流<br />\n<br />\n[和你飛] 外國人旅遊，中國人滯留<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1463771\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1463771</a><br />\n<br />\n離境大堂被阻外國人：應該控制，而唔係阻止登記<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1463192\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1463192</a>"},{"pid":"70ae918789a11c71132ceb2e07d17cf33b5faa73","tid":1465663,"uid":12180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:17:13.000Z","msg":"唔覺，可以集中講警察同公安臥底搞事<br />\n停止失敗言論"},{"pid":"17e045f80db132bea07f3679b5dd260f204c4f98","tid":1465663,"uid":22632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:17:17.000Z","msg":"屌 根本某d人無哂理性"},{"pid":"41075eac27b05c084c8b05ca2b7432671255699d","tid":1465663,"uid":32655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:17:27.000Z","msg":"唔好分化呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0c3cdc83c0f8157e8f1871781ee7c9d0e161ba7","tid":1465663,"uid":119485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:17:38.000Z","msg":"捱到星期五 周末就得<br />\n加油！"},{"pid":"14534d268d4254dd6de2b3329d7ff4ea97abe046","tid":1465663,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:17:50.000Z","msg":"呢招真係好毒。<br />\n佢任你屌, 無還過手, <br />\n頂你30分鐘, 硬食幾十拳, <br />\n<br />\n最後先扮死, <br />\n真心高明"},{"pid":"85